to send you home now.

96
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:01,080
Let's get the cafe ready.

97
00:05:01,100 --> 00:05:03,480
Go, go get the
chair off the table first.

98
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,540
OK.

99
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,210
