103
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,880
What are you talking about?

104
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,610
No need to act like you don't know.

105
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:32,390
I can tell.

106
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:33,780
Your eyes...

107
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:35,790
your behavior...

108
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,870
it shows that you like Kok.

109
00:05:40,890 --> 00:05:42,730
If I really do like him...

110
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,210
So...

111
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:45,710
what's it to you?

112
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:48,190
Nothing.

113
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,970
But if Kok knows...

114
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,430
what will happen?

115
00:05:56,690 --> 00:05:58,670
You're threatening me.

116
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,710
No!

117
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:02,660
Let me tell you something.

118
00:06:02,690 --> 00:06:04,170
The reason Kok is being nice to you...

119
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,050
is because he feels guilty.

120
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:08,150
The same way you
feel guilty towards him.

121
00:06:08,850 --> 00:06:10,180
What are you talking about?

122
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,080
What feeling guilty?!

123
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:14,850
It's about you cause him to
get kicked out by his aunt.

124
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,270
because he
took the blame for you.

125
00:06:17,850 --> 00:06:19,680
How do you know that?

126
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:22,050
It's not important.

127
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,510
Let's just say that I know.

128
00:06:23,610 --> 00:06:26,010
That you had a
fight with Kok's aunt's son.

129
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,650
Because that kid
said that Kok is an orphan.

130
00:06:29,170 --> 00:06:30,600
So Kok helped you...

131
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:31,890
took the blame in your place.

132
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,440
Because he knows that you're causing
trouble to him so Kok protected him.

133
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:37,090
From that moment on,
he's being nice to you.

134
00:06:37,110 --> 00:06:38,450
But do you know something?

135
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,520
He doesn't have any feelings for you.

136
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:43,000
