with you always sticking around to him.

137
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:44,820
But he has to endure it.

138
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:50,880
I don't care how much you know.

139
00:06:51,460 --> 00:06:52,700
Besides...

140
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,400
I don't believe...

141
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,200
that Kok being nice to me...

142
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,930
because he feels guilty.

143
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:05,190
