149
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,830
No one can come in between.

150
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:25,000
Or do you want to get in between?

151
00:07:26,610 --> 00:07:28,400
Let me tell you something.

152
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:30,590
It's probably a little hard.

153
00:07:40,260 --> 00:07:41,580
Try harder.

154
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,470
I have to go now.

155
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,470
Uncle, hear me out.

156
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:06,560
Move.

157
00:08:06,590 --> 00:08:07,720
I won't.

158
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:09,340
Until you stop angry at me first.

159
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:12,170
I told you, I'm not angry. Let me go!

160
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:14,910
I'm not letting you go.

161
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:17,110
I said let me go!

162
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,290
You're not gonna
stop angry at me, right?

163
00:08:27,590 --> 00:08:28,710
Go.

164
00:08:29,730 --> 00:08:31,490
Do you forgive me yet?

165
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,490
Yes!

166
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:36,020
I am.

167
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:38,170
Then...

168
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:39,370
