208
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,870
I don't know.

209
00:11:00,690 --> 00:11:02,390
He definitely isn't into me.

210
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:05,310
He doesn't like me, 100%, 1000%.

211
00:11:07,040 --> 00:11:08,270
Alright, alright.

212
00:11:09,580 --> 00:11:11,430
If you say it like that...

213
00:11:11,590 --> 00:11:13,090
