267
00:15:11,810 --> 00:15:13,010
I'm not happy...

268
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:15,070
when someone
else stick close to you.

269
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:16,210
That's it.

270
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,480
I don't like it!

271
00:15:18,090 --> 00:15:19,890
